data.description: Beautiful Treed Entrance Welcomes Country Living & Convenience. This 16AC with a 3/2/2 Carport is fenced and cross fenced. Split Floorplan. Open kitchen with Island/Bar. Oversized Pantry. Fireplace in Eat-in Kitchen & Formal Living/Dining Room. Inviting Master Bath with Separate Shower & garden tub. Outside conveys a large 10x30 Storage Bldg and a detached 400SF bldg on Slab that has the potential to be a man cave/game room or apt. has Water & electric in place. The back portion makes for excellent for hunting.
